---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About - Chiara Pia D'Ambrosio">
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="two-column">
        <div class="profile-section">
          <img 
            src="/assets/profile-image.jpeg" 
            alt="Chiara Pia D'Ambrosio" 
            class="profile-image"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="bio-section">
          <h1>About Me</h1>
          <p>
            Welcome to my academic website. I am a Doctoral Student in Strategy & Entrepreneurship at London Business School. 
            My research focuses on strategic management and entrepreneurship, with particular interest in organizational behavior 
            and business strategy.
          </p>
          <p>
            I hold a BSc in Finance and an MSc in Accounting, Financial Management and Control from Bocconi University. 
            Currently, I am pursuing a PhD in Strategy & Entrepreneurship at London Business School (2022-2027). 
            My academic journey has been enriched by exchange programs at Rotterdam School of Management and 
            Indiana University - Kelley School of Business.
          </p>
          <p>
            Prior to my doctoral studies, I gained valuable industry experience working as a Controller at Luxottica, 
            a Research Assistant at SDA Bocconi, and an Audit Assistant at PwC. This combination of academic rigor 
            and practical experience informs my research approach and teaching philosophy.
          </p>
          
          <!-- Contact Section -->
          <div class="contact-section">
            <div class="contact-links">
              <a href="mailto:cdambrosio@london.edu" class="contact-link" title="Send Email">
                <div class="contact-icon">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
